    "In the context of EWSs, gamification can be used to gather data from the public, such as through apps that turn data collection into a game-like experience, e.g.",
    "with examples from previous disasters.",
    "In addition, the interactive EWS-FM chatbot can be used to gather a wealth of important, representative and high-quality data.",
    "This can lead to more comprehensive and real-time data collection, providing a richer dataset for predicting long-term effects and societal responses to warnings.",
    "Integration into policy for long duration warnings: Integrating EWSs with policy-making processes for long-term planning is crucial."
